# Components

All components live in `src/components/`. They read from the Zustand store via `useGraphStore` and dispatch mutations through store methods — no local state for graph data.

## Responsibilities

| Component             | Role                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
| --------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| `GraphCanvas`         | React Flow canvas. Wires `nodeTypes`, `edgeTypes`, `connectionLineComponent` (`NessoConnectionLine`), store change handlers. Respects inset props; `onMoveEnd` saves viewport to the store (`saveViewport`). Optional `onViewportZoomChange` drives the bottom-dock zoom `%` (wheel, +/-, fit, graph switch). |
| `ConceptNode`         | Custom node. Renders text; optional **`showHeatmap`** overlay uses last rating colours (`--conf-*`). Underline encodes last rating (`showConfidence`); dashed when the card is due (`reps > 0` and `due <= now`). Inline rename as before. Handle ids `out` / `in`.                                           |
| `NessoConnectionLine` | Custom connection preview while dragging a new edge: same quadratic geometry as `NessoEdge`, starts at the handle under the cursor (left vs right).                                                                                                                                                           |
| `NessoEdge`           | Custom edge. Draws line with style (solid/dashed/dotted/double/wavy) and end glyph based on `EdgeTypeDef`. Respects `edgeEncoding` setting.                                                                                                                                                                   |
| `GlyphSVG`            | Pure SVG renderer for the 16 `GlyphKind` icons used on edges.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
| `TopBar`              | Top chrome when sidebar is open: graph **title**, concept/link counts. When sidebar is **collapsed**, icon-only control to expand the **Sidebar**. Right: **Review** pill (icon + **R**); **⋯** menu (`GraphIO`) for relation types, JSON export/import, and keyboard shortcuts.                              |
| `Sidebar`             | Left strip: brand, icon **collapse**, search (**⌘K**), graph list (**New** + rows), recent concepts, **Display** toggles (heatmap, etc.; theme is in Settings), footer **Settings** (⌘,) full-width row.                                                                                                      |
| `SearchDialog`        | Command-palette style search (**⌘K** / **Ctrl+K**). Filters concept labels; **Enter** or click selects, closes, recenters viewport on the node via `App` `setCenter`. Concept rows show a four-dot hint from `lastRating`. Escape / backdrop like other overlays.                                             |
| `GraphIO`             | Top-bar **⋯** menu: open relation types, export JSON, import JSON (`importGraph`), keyboard shortcuts. Receives `onRelationTypes` / `onShortcuts` callbacks from `App` via `TopBar`.                                                                                                                          |
| `BottomDock`          | Fixed bottom dock. Fit/center graph, zoom in/out/percent label, **+ concept**.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
| `RelationTypesDialog` | Centered modal (same shell as `ShortcutsDialog` / `SettingsDialog`). Relation-type reference; opened from `GraphIO` or elsewhere via `App`; header `CloseButton`.                                                                                                                                             |
| `Inspector`           | Left panel when a node or edge is selected. **Concept:** edits `text`; shows FSRS due / stability / last rating. **Edge:** type chips.                                                                                                                                                                        |
| `RelationPicker`      | Dropdown grid for selecting an `EdgeTypeName`. Groups by `EdgeCategory`.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |
| `MentorBubble`        | FAB + card. Single **Socratic chat** over the graph (nodes + edges + selection context); no mode tabs. `mentorPanelExpanded` persisted. Root `pointer-events: none`; FAB/card `auto`. FSRS ratings happen only in **ReviewMode**. See `mentor.mdc`.                                                           |
| `SocratesGlyph`       | SVG avatar for Socrates (used in `MentorBubble`).                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |
| `ReviewMode`          | Full-screen overlay. Queues due concepts via **`sortedDueConceptNodes`** (`dailyNewLimit` + `dailyStudyCounters`). Again/Hard/Good/Easy → `recordStudyRating` + `scheduler.next` via `nodeToCard`.                                                                                                            |
| `ShortcutsDialog`     | Overlay listing keyboard shortcuts (**?** key or `GraphIO` menu). Header `CloseButton`; closes on backdrop or Escape (`App`).                                                                                                                                                                                 |
| `SettingsDialog`      | Overlay: tabbed **Appearance**, **AI**, **Review** (`fsrsRetention`, `dailyNewLimit`, `maximumInterval`, etc.). Gear / **⌘,**; header `CloseButton`.                                                                                                                                                          |
| `CloseButton`         | Icon dismiss for modal headers (`SettingsDialog`, `ShortcutsDialog`, `RelationTypesDialog`).                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |

## Layout

`App.tsx` renders all panels over a single `position: fixed; inset: 0` root. `GraphCanvas` receives inset props so the React Flow viewport avoids panel overlap — panels do not clip the canvas, they just narrow the usable area. `leftInset` widens when the `Inspector` is visible; relation types are a modal, not an inset panel.

## No prop drilling

Components read global state directly from `useGraphStore`. Do not add props for data that is already in the store — add a selector instead.
